{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTTP/3","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTTP_3","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li>一般知識\n  <ol>\n   <li>MDN 上の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP\">HTTP</a></li>\n   <li>Wikipedia 上の <a title=\"HTTP/3\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTTP/3\">HTTP/3</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary\">用語集</a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTTP\">HTTP</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTTP_2\">HTTP/2</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Latency\">Latency</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>HTTP/3</strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTTP_2\">HTTP/2</a> に続く <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Basics_of_HTTP\">HTTP ネットワークプロトコル</a> の今後のメジャーリビジョンです。</span> HTTP/3 の主なポイントは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/TCP\">TCP</a> の代わりに QUIC という新しい <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/UDP\">UDP</a> プロトコルを使用することです。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"HTTP/3 は HTTP/2 に続く HTTP ネットワークプロトコル の今後のメジャーリビジョンです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTTP/3","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTTP/3","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTTP/3","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTTP/3","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/http_3","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/http_3/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTTP_3","title":"HTTP/3"}],"pageTitle":"HTTP/3 - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}